I&#x27;ve seen multiple &quot;Ask HN&quot; threads here on HN asking:
&quot;what app&#x2F;software&#x2F;tool&#x2F;x you wish existed&quot;<p>Examples:
&quot;What game do you wish existed&quot;
&quot;What “missing” technical solution(s) do you wish existed&quot;
&quot;What products or services do you wish existed for your startup?&quot;
&quot;What are some APIs you wish existed?&quot;
etc.<p>What to you think of a website (subreddit?) where people would post their ideas and vote for other people&#x27;s ideas? Then maybe get in touch to develop &#x2F; fund?
